p.01703376c4a81c0e9d91: A sample library of bricks, used by Sample applications
p.01703376c4a81c0e9d92:
This library contains two bricks and a test application.

Demonstrated concepts
----------
Setting the visibility on bricks to build a library of reusable logic and visual components.

Building your own
----------
Any project can be transformed into a library of bricks by setting its `Visibility` property to `This project can be imported by other projects as a library`

The `Help Button` visual component is set as `Public` and can therefore be used in other projects.

The `Format Popup Text` function is *not* set as `Public` and can therefore *not* be used in other projects.

You can try it out by going to your project's `Dependencies` tab of your project.importing this project into your own project
